        >
          Still on Windows 10? The final safety net ends this&nbsp;October
        </h1>

        <p
          class="alien-font"
          style="font-size: 19px; color: var(--comet-silver); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 750px;"
        >
          Windows 10's extended security updates stop for good on 13 October 2026 — and this
          time there's no extension behind it. Here's how to check where you stand, and an
          honest look at your options: upgrade, refurbish, or replace.
        </p>

        <div class="article-meta tech-font">
          <div class="meta-item">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
